{%- doc -%}
  Renders a single gradient-filled star icon for the "Customer reviews tabs"
  section. All stars in the section share one <linearGradient> (defined once
  by the section itself) to avoid repeating/duplicating SVG ids.

  @param {string} section_id - The id of the gradient to reference.
  @param {string} [class] - Optional extra class on the <svg>.

  @example
  {% render 'customer-reviews-tabs-star', section_id: section.id %}
{%- enddoc -%}

